}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The device may not actually be using a standard PCMCIA interface, but it is using the same connector and has the same form factor. It lacks the CardBus strip.
This module is used in the [[D-Link DI-714P+ rev B1]].
There is an additional model listed as CNDS11g in the FCC test report.
